==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Doom palm
<hw>Doom" palm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Ar. <ets>daum</ets>,
<ets>d⟦umac⟧m</ets>: cf. F. <ets>doume</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A species of palm tree (<spn>Hyph⟦ae⟧ne Thebaica</spn>), highly
valued for the fibrous pulp of its fruit, which has the flavor of
gingerbread, and is largely eaten in Egypt and Abyssinia.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>doum palm</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Doomsday</ent>⟦br⟧
